 They carried out search and rescue in the affected area,

646
00:42:54,800 --> 00:42:59,000
 prevented secondary disasters, transferred the trapped people, built tents,

647
00:42:59,000 --> 00:43:02,600
 organized medical treatment centers to treat the people there.

648
00:43:02,600 --> 00:43:06,200
 The emergency center has implemented traffic control on roads leading to Fengxi,

649
00:43:06,200 --> 00:43:07,600
 to guarantee emergency access,

650
00:43:07,600 --> 00:43:09,200
 and has fully launched emergency communication,

651
00:43:09,200 --> 00:43:10,700
